2. Why is subscription renewal a classification problem?
Subscription renewal is a classification problem because the target has two categories:
->Renew (Yes)
->Not Renew (No)

3.Why is monthly spending a regression problem?
Monthly spending is a regression problem because MonthlySpend is a continuous numerical value (₹300, ₹700, ₹1000, etc.).Regression 
is used when predicting numerical quantities

